Rush talking about the march being "conservative" was him saying that they are sick of the government. Since the current Admin is Democrat that the opposition is obviously a conservative opposition (though I do disagree with that personally)

Trick here is your problem, you rely on others informing you rather than hearing him yourself. What rush said id that they had no official leader, meaning a grassroots march, it had no formal party or orginazation pushing it. Just because glen beck "lead the charge" does not mean it was not a grassroots effort. Rush never claimed that no one would "lead the charge" you cant prove that he did.
